These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 5

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-5-1::.
House: art-deco, cape-cod
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: dubstep, reggae
1. the cape-cod house is somewhere to the left of the fan of dubstep##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |
| House           | cape-cod | art-deco |
| Music-Genre   | reggae     | dubstep  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-5-2::.
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: swisher, blend
The people use 2 different means of transport: airplane, motorbike
1. the person driving the airplane is somewhere to the left of the swisher-smoker##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1     |     2     |
| Cigar         | blend   | swisher      |
| Transport   | airplane | motorbike |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-5-3::.
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: r&b, rock
There are 2 different nationalities: colombian, italian
1. the fan of r&b is somewhere to the right of the colombian##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |   2    |
| Music-Genre   | rock | r&b    |
| Nationality     | colombian | italian |

