1. the person eating cauliflower is somewhere to the left of the person drinking juice##5
2. the person drinking juice is on the right of the person drinking tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |
| Beverage      | tea        | juice  |
| Food   | cauliflower | strawberry |

